    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried calling them and they were so cold. they just told me they have strict policies and won't budge without immediate payment. it feels like the system is just designed to crush people like me. there's no \"hardship program\" that actually works when you're already bottomed out. honestly, it feels like there's no math that makes this add up. is there any way to actually protect my family or my assets before everything is gone?",
